name: Kelvin
description: I’m always myself,I don’t claim to be what i am not. I tend to speak my mind and share more light and thoughts to things, I’m not perfect, I’m a good listener and I like learn. I am a caring, loving, understanding man. I like the outdoors, sports, taking walks, movies, music, and spending time at home. I have a great sense of humor. I love life and I love to laugh. I am looking for a serious relationship. I am looking for a woman who is serious and wants to be loved and treated like a queen.
